{"tid":56814,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"《天堂》系列手機新作《天堂 M》官網上線 經典角色死亡騎士現身","createTime":"2016-12-27T14:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T02:24:47.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d20b77c75acb8d946d39c9860409274616cf3d4","tid":56814,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"NCSOFT 基於《天堂》世界觀所打造的手機新作《天堂 M（Lineage M）》韓國官網於今日稍早正式上線，玩家可以看到死亡騎士手持武器，傲然站立於戰場上的英姿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/45/0001488545.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F45%2F0001488545.JPG&h=7a2ac8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《天堂 M》雖是一款手機遊戲，但玩家將可在本作上體驗到以往於 PC 版中遊玩到的內容，如野外 PVP 與攻城戰等內容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/46/0001488546.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F46%2F0001488546.JPG&h=da191f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《天堂 M》目前尚未公開遊戲上市時間，欲知更多後續消息請密切注意後續報導。<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/8/141778.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F8%2F141778.html&d=n5f1urfBbF4NdF4zZ9erVQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8129ab12\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/8/141778.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3e13ef0757800eae836b6bd48f934284b44363a","tid":56814,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d16592656e17c195dd3cb4273f8627fa5a067d42","tid":56814,"uid":60322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}